Arguments

.sutdata

a data frame of supply-use table matrices with matrices arranged in columns.
method_q_calculation

Specifies the method which with the q vector should be calculated. Default is sum_U_Y_rows. Alternatively, an analyst can choose to use the sum_R_V_cols method. In the case of a balanced ECC, the method does not matter.
R

resources (R) matrix or name of the column in .sutmats that contains same. Default is "R".
U

use (U) matrix or name of the column in `.sutmats`` that contains same. Default is "U".
U_feed

use matrix or name of the column in .sutmats that contains same. Default is "U_feed".
V

make (V) matrix or name of the column in .sutmatsthat contains same. Default is "V".
Y

final demand (Y) matrix or name of the column in .sutmats that contains same. Default is "Y".
S_units

(S_units) matrix or name of the column in .sutmats that contains same. Default is "S_units".
y

name for y vector on output. Default is "y". y is calculated by rowsums(Y).
q

name for q vector on output. Default is "q". q is calculated by rowsums(U) + y.
f

name for f vector on output. Default is "f". f is calculated by colsums(U).
g

name for g vector on output. Default is "g". g is calculated by rowsums(V).
W

name for W matrix on output. Default is "W". W is calculated by transpose(V) - U.
K

name for K matrix on output. Default is "K". K is calculated by U * f_hat_inv.
Z

name for Z matrix on output. Default is "Z". Z is calculated by U * g_hat_inv.
C

name for C matrix on output. Default is "C". C is calculated by transpose(V) * g_hat_inv.
D

name for D matrix on output. Default is "D". D is calculated by V * q_hat_inv.
A

name for A matrix on output. Default is "A". A is calculated by Z * D.
L_ixp

name for L_ixp matrix on output. Default is "L_ixp". L_ixp is calculated by D * L_pxp.
L_pxp

name for L_pxp_feed matrix on output. Default is "L_pxp_feed". L_pxp is calculated by (I - Z*D)^-1.
Z_feed

name for Z_feed matrix on output. Default is "Z_feed". Z_feed is calculated by U_feed * g_hat_inv.
K_feed

name for K_feed matrix on output. Default is "K_feed". K_feed is calculated by U_feed * f_hat_inv.
C_feed

name for C_feed matrix on output. Default is "C_feed". C_feed is calculated by transpose(V) * g_hat_inv.
D_feed

name for D_feed matrix on output. Default is "D_feed". D_feed is calculated by V * q_hat_inv.
A_feed

name for A_feed matrix on output. Default is "A_feed". A_feed is calculated by Z_feed * D_feed.
L_ixp_feed

name for L_ixp_feed matrix on output. Default is "L_ixp_feed". L_ixp_feed is calculated by D_feed * L_pxp_feed.
L_pxp_feed

name for L_pxp_feed matrix on output. Default is "L_pxp_feed". L_pxp_feed is calculated by (I - Z_feed*D)^-1.

Value

a list or data frame containing input-output matrices
